_summary":"M Lakhamsi Industries Limited engages in trading and processing oil and oil seeds in India and internationally. It offers peanut, sesame, castor, safflower, sunflower, oriental and yellow mustard, and soybean; pulses, including chick peas, brown chick peas, pigeon peas, yellow and green peas, red and green lentils, green mung, black eyed beans, kidney beans, and black matpe. The company also provides grains, such as sorghum, wheat, rice, maize, and millet; spices comprising chilli whole and flakes, turmeric fingers and powders, fenugreek, dill, and chilli powder; and oil and oilcakes consisting of mustard, sesame, peanut, and castor oil, as well as oil cakes. In addition, it offers golden, brown, and black raisins; and natural gum and sugar. The company was formerly known as Specular Marketing & Financing Limited and changed its name to M Lakhamsi Industries Limited in August 2021. M Lakhamsi Industries Limited was incorporated in 1985 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}